bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u>，<u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;。</u><br />（7）《水调歌头》中表达作者美好祝愿的句子<u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u>，<u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;。</u></p>\n                        <p class=\"btns\">\n<a href=\'/quest/cTMyM__wMj4M.html\' target=_blank class=\"paper_viewall\">答案与解析</a>\n                        <a class=\"paper_viewall to-zujuan\" href=\"http://zujuan.21cnjy.com/\" target=\"_blank\" alt=\"在线组卷\">在线组卷</a>\n                        <p>\n<div id=\'an_9\' style=\"display: none;\"> <b>答案：</b>-<br/><b>解析：</b>-</div>\n</div><h3> 书写</h3>\n\n              \n             \n <div class=\"shiti\">\n<p>根据拼音写汉字（4分）<br />学语文没有一劳永yì（&nbsp;）的方法，只要你有qiè（&nbsp;）而不舍的恒心,páo（&nbsp;）根问底的决心，bó（&nbsp;）览群书的耐心，就一定能学好它。<br /><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr style=\"height:14.5pt\"><td width=\"21\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:15.65pt;border-top:solid;border-left: solid;border-bottom:dashed;border-right:dashed;border-color:windowtext; border-width:1.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.5pt\">&nbsp;<br /><address  title=\'tiku.21cnjy.com\' class=\"this_jammer\">& h1 F- U0 P# e$ H7 T( e</address> </td><td width=\"21\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:15.65pt;border-top:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left:none;border-bottom:dashed windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.5pt\">&nbsp;<br /><address  title=\'tiku.21cnjy.com\' class=\"this_jammer\">& h1 F- U0 P# e$ H7 T( e</address> </td><td width=\"21\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:15.65pt;border-top:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left:none;border-bottom:dashed windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:dashed windowtext 1.0pt; padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.5pt\">&nbsp;<br /><address  title=\'tiku.21cnjy.com\' class=\"this_jammer\">& h1 F- U0 P# e$ H7 T( e</address> </td><td width=\"21\" valig